name: Artistic Expressions
description: A 3464 x 3464 jpg image created with my own unique design and algorithm to create the artistic visual of emotions you see before you. This was inspired by the way we humans seem to get hyper focused on petty, small, unimportant things that become the singularity of our stress. Then we circle around that stress trying to find ways to block it instead of taking the problem on head first. Those that do break the cycle are far more happy and live stress free lives. This represents my struggle with that very problem.
